  Aegis OS — live environment (Arch-based, stock kernel).
  The sphere kiosk runs on tty1 as user 'aegis'. This console is another VT.

  Install to disk ....  pick "Install Aegis OS" at the boot menu,
                        or from here: sudo aegis-installer
  Agent status .......  systemctl status aegis-agent
  Kiosk (greetd) .....  systemctl status greetd
  Audio devices ......  sudo -u aegis pactl list short sinks
  Network ............  already up via systemd-networkd / iwctl for Wi-Fi
